IMPORT math

' bug-137: a Fixed base with |base| < 1 raised to a large-magnitude negative
' exponent underflows the forward product to 0, so the reciprocal 1.0/0.0 is a
' genuine range overflow. It must trap ErrOverflow, not ErrInvalidArgument.
FUNC main() AS Integer
  math::pow(0.5F, 0.0F - 80.0F)
  RETURN 0
END FUNC
